{"tid":1696484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇和理非個口同鍵盤話不割，但個心已經偷偷割左","createTime":"2019-11-06T07:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T16:57:21.000Z","uid":203248,"like":3,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a922e7da7d10bb8747b57f26cd391a0a31620075","tid":1696484,"uid":203248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"其實暴力越嚟越升級，基本上每次示威，都搞到越嚟越少人出嚟， 運動流失支持， 完全再冇和理非嘅回合，咁我地都好難再出黎。加上好多人已經係ig post返飲飲食食，運動已經去到樽頸位。前幾日科大生命危，加上今日何君堯俾人差d殺死， 好普通嘅和理非都會覺得使唔使去到咁盡去到攞人命，完全喪失曬理智。大部分和理非個口同鍵盤話不割，但個心已經偷偷割左了，你睇每次出黎越嚟越少人就知。有少少良知嘅都知係暴力係唔啱，身邊有好多和理非同我有同樣想法，唔想再見到有香港人受傷。"},{"pid":"6df0b8f83002acc2ffe1a3db12e2e7a6135f07c3","tid":1696484,"uid":202131,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"何君堯俾人差啲殺死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faeef8599ca978d87592017a55cd2764489a59b","tid":1696484,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:57:10.000Z","msg":"低級spin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n何妖遇襲 極可能係為區選扮弱者+幫警分散科大事件，請冷處理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1695860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1695860</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d72962c82bce869b981798d03b186420e589d771","tid":1696484,"uid":35420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:57:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 請善用起底功能</span>"},{"pid":"e6ab598aafa99c119388e126ea5c74cd29ecbfcb","tid":1696484,"uid":203248,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"6df0b8f83002acc2ffe1a3db12e2e7a6135f07c3","tid":1696484,"uid":202131,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"何君堯俾人差啲殺死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"把刀直筒心臟比肋骨擋住，差1cm死人"},{"pid":"a699e9cf4e